om the Centre for Economic and Social Inclusion by the Local Government Association </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">Tony Wilson, Gareth Morgan, Afzal Rahman, Lovedeep Vaid, August 2013 available from http://www.local.gov.uk/c/document</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">_library</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn12"></a><a href="#_ftnref12">[12]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> Statistical Data Return, published August 2012, Homes and Communities Agency available from http://www.homesandcommunities.co.uk/news/statistical-data-return </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn13"></a><a href="#_ftnref13">[13]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> Ibid</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn14"></a><a href="#_ftnref14">[14]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> www.parliament.uk/briefing-papers/sn06272.pdf</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">&#x200e;</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn15"></a><a href="#_ftnref15">[15]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">Thousands of carers hit by </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">charge struggling to pay their bills, charity warns</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">, Daily Mirror, 10 July 2013 - </span><a href="http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/bedroom-tax-thousands-carers-hit-2041390"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline">http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/bedroom-tax-thousands-carers-hit-2041390</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn16"></a><a href="#_ftnref16">[16]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">National Housing Federation analysis </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:nor